<figureCitation id="136BEF9AFFCCF13C42986C2FFF1CFEEE" box="[151,235,331,357]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1591,1615]" captionTargetBox="[182,1405,179,1550]" captionTargetId="figure-24@6.[182,1405,179,1565]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 1. Neotropical Sclerodermus, holotype females, habitus in dorsal view. A. S. domesticus; B. S. galapagensis; C. S. iridomyrmicicola; D. S. macrogaster; E. S. spilonotum; F. S. soror; G. S. wilsoni.; H. S. chicomendesi sp. nov. Scale-bars: 100µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6416946" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6416946/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="506">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
